Publicis Buys U.K.’s Holler Ad Agency to Increase Digital Sales

-- B y   K r i s t e n   S c h w e i z e r
-- 
2011-02-17T07:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/publicis-buys-u-k-s-holler-ad-agency-to-increase-digital-sales.html
  Publicis Groupe SA  said it acquired
the Holler digital ad agency in  London  to enhance the digital
capability at its Leo Burnett Group in the U.K.  Holler, which specializes in social media and branded
entertainment, works with clients including Red Bull, Global
Radio and Channel 4, Publicis said in a statement today. No
purchase price was disclosed.  The acquisition is part of Publicis’s plan to expand
revenue from digital activities. Publicis is aiming to gain
35 percent of its revenue from digital in three years, up from
28 percent now, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kristen Schweizer in London at 
 kschweizer1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at   vroot@bloomberg.net . 